originalText.text: The worst Foster care agency ever. My daughter just killed herself and that is greatly due then knowing she was homeless and not securing a place for her to live when she aged out. Do not send your vulnerable kids here

text.text: The worst Foster care agency ever. My daughter just killed herself and that is greatly due then knowing she was homeless and not securing a place for her to live when she aged out. Do not send your vulnerable kids here

originalText.text: My kids been through about 5 case planners and each has left without a word and without debriefing the next planner. Even they don’t want to deal with that agency. It feels more like they are there to punish you rather than help you because I have never experienced such inconsistency and laziness. Both my kids are autistic and my oldest has REGRESSED and spent a whole year without school and services. My youngest was diagnosed while with the agency and is getting help about a year after diagnosis. There should be no reason why I have to seek help from outside sources to get my kids the help they need. Always unprepared for court and never know what’s going on or how to help. One of those agencies you have to harass to get things done. Poor quality staff and depressing atmosphere. My life is so much worse after dealing with them. I can’t wait to get my kids back. NEVER AGAIN. I LEARNED.
